		{"id":"5db67a17d99d7acc","type":"text","text":"自然是善的，人性是善的，只是社会把人变坏了。","x":-735,"y":-178,"width":295,"height":91},
		{"id":"1364b70a6273db6c","type":"text","text":"世界之外无书籍，事实以外无教材","x":335,"y":-178,"width":250,"height":91},
		{"id":"43aab20501eda6af","type":"text","text":"自然主义教育","x":-179,"y":0,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"9666ae7358d1f7ee","type":"text","text":"卢梭","x":-105,"y":-340,"width":131,"height":65,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"0f7ad534f456badd","type":"text","text":"正确看待儿童","x":-327,"y":361,"width":130,"height":81,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"dd3d940b514b37e0","type":"text","text":"基本含义","x":-1015,"y":213,"width":280,"height":60,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"32fc519009ab217f","type":"text","text":"**只有“归于自然”的教育，远离喧嚣城市社会的教育，才有利于保持人的善良天性**。因此 15 岁之前的教育必须在远离城市的农村中进行。","x":-1015,"y":329,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"0cc0bb0d15911086","type":"text","text":"**最终培养目标是“自然人”**：\n- 独立自主\n- 平等\n- 自由\n- 自食其力","x":-700,"y":216,"width":301,"height":226,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"d9a4feb2abc63084","type":"text","text":"方法原则","x":-262,"y":213,"width":157,"height":60,"color":"2"},
